'''1971年印巴战争'''，也被称为'''第三次印巴战争'''，是1971年12月[[印度|印度]]与[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]两国之间的战争。该战争与[[孟加拉国独立战争|孟加拉国独立战争]]密切相关。

印度、孟加拉及國際上一般認為巴基斯坦在1971年12月3日空襲11個印度空軍基地的「[[成吉思汗行動|成吉思汗行動]]」是這次戰爭的開始。<ref name=LATimes>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2002/mar/30/local/me-passings30.1|title=Gen. Tikka Khan, 87; 'Butcher of Bengal' Led Pakistani Army|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=11 April 2010|date=30 March 2002|archive-date=2012-03-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/664trrihU?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2002/mar/30/local/me-passings30.1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IoP">{{cite book|last=Cohen|first=Stephen|title=The Idea of Pakistan|year=2004|page=382|isbn=978-0-8157-1502-3|url=http://books.google.com/?id=-78yjVybQfkC&lpg=PP1&dq=Google%20books%20The%20idea%20of%20Pakistan%20%2F%20Stephen%20Philip%20Cohen&pg=PA8#v=onepage&q|publisher=Brookings Institution Press|access-date=2012-04-07|archive-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128024736/http://books.google.com/?id=-78yjVybQfkC&lpg=PP1&dq=Google%20books%20The%20idea%20of%20Pakistan%20%2F%20Stephen%20Philip%20Cohen&pg=PA8#v=onepage&q|dead-url=no}}</ref>

戰爭期間，印度與巴基斯坦的軍隊在東部和西部戰場交戰。當[[東巴基斯坦|東巴基斯坦]]（今孟加拉國）的巴基斯坦軍隊在1971年12月16日投降時，戰爭在實質上結束，东巴基斯坦亦脫離巴基斯坦成為一個獨立主权國家。在東巴基斯坦，約9萬名巴國武裝部隊人員，包括準軍事人員成為戰俘。<ref name="mosq-mill">{{cite book|last = Haqqani|first = Hussain|title = Pakistan: Between Mosque and Military|url=http://books.google.com/?id=nYppZ_dEjdIC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q=|year=2005|publisher = United Book Press|isbn = 978-0-87003-214-1}}, Chapter 3, pp 87.</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Burke|first=Samuel Martin|title=Mainsprings of Indian and Pakistani Foreign Policies|year=1974|publisher=University Of Minnesota Press|isbn=978-0-8166-5714-8|pages=216|url=http://books.google.com.pk/books?id=nuYcwYCcjpIC&lpg=PA216&ots=2KhNYIAi28&dq=15%2C000%20pakistani%20women%20prisoner%20of%20war%201971&pg=PA216#v=onepage&q=15,000%20pakistani%20women%20prisoner%20of%20war%201971&f=false|access-date=2012-04-07|archive-date=2013-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524115120/http://books.google.com.pk/books?id=nuYcwYCcjpIC&lpg=PA216&ots=2KhNYIAi28&dq=15%2C000%20pakistani%20women%20prisoner%20of%20war%201971&pg=PA216#v=onepage&q=15,000%20pakistani%20women%20prisoner%20of%20war%201971&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==

這次印度與巴基斯坦的衝突由[[孟加拉國獨立戰爭|孟加拉國獨立戰爭]]引發。

1971年3月27日，巴基斯坦軍隊一名少校[[齊亞·拉赫曼|齊亞·拉赫曼]]以[[謝赫·穆吉布·拉赫曼|謝赫·穆吉布·拉赫曼]]的名義宣佈孟加拉獨立。<ref name=Qureshi>{{cite book|last=Qureshi|first=Hakeem Arshad|title=Through the 1971 Crisis: An Eyewitness Account by a Soldier|year=2003|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-579778-7|pages=33}}</ref>4月，[[孟加拉國人民聯盟|孟加拉國人民聯盟]]領導人在[[梅黑爾布爾縣|梅黑爾布爾縣]]成立一個臨時政府。[[孟加拉国步枪队|東巴基斯坦步槍隊]]變節支持叛亂者。由正規軍及游擊隊組成的孟加拉部隊「解放軍」成立。<ref>Raja, Dewan Mohammad Tasawwar, ''O GENERAL MY GENERAL (Life and Works of General M A G Osmany)'', p35-109, ISBN 978-984-8866-18-4</ref>

==印度在孟加拉國獨立戰爭的參與==
巴基斯坦軍隊在東巴基斯坦發動[[探照燈行動|探照燈行動]]，進行針對[[孟加拉族|孟加拉族]]的屠殺，<ref name="uspol">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,878970,00.html|title=The U.S.: A Policy in Shambles|work=Time Magazine, 20 December 1971|publisher=|accessdate=2009-10-20|date=20 December 1971|archive-date=2013-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824114059/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,878970,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>特別是印度教徒少數族裔、知識分子及民族主義者，<ref name="usconsulate_cable_march31">U.S. Consulate (Dacca) Cable, Sitrep: [http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/NSAEBB/NSAEBB79/BEBB6.pdf Army Terror Campaign Continues in Dacca; Evidence Military Faces Some Difficulties Elsewhere] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/NSAEBB/NSAEBB79/BEBB6.pdf |date=20111221082405 }}, 31 March 1971, Confidential, 3 pp.</ref><ref name="time.oct25-1971">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,877316,00.html|title=East Pakistan: Even the Skies Weep|work=Time Magazine, 25 October 1971|publisher=|accessdate=2009-10-20|date=25 October 1971|archive-date=2009-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091008112352/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,877316,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>引致約1000萬人<ref name="usconsulate_cable_march31" /><ref name="tie">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,905593,00.html|title=India: Easy Victory, Uneasy Peace|work=Time Magazine, 27 December 1971|publisher=|accessdate=2009-10-20|date=27 December 1971|archive-date=2013-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824113905/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,905593,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>從東巴基斯坦逃入印度避難。<ref name="uspol" /><ref name="MSN Encarta">{{cite encyclopedia|url=http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761588350_3/Indo-Pakistani_Wars.html#s29|title=Indo-Pakistani Wars|work=MSN Encarta|accessdate=2009-10-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5kwrHv6ph?url=http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761588350_3/Indo-Pakistani_Wars.html#s29|archivedate=2009-11-01|deadurl=yes}}</ref>這股難民潮在經濟上對印度構成沉重負擔。<ref name="time.oct25-1971" />

印度總理[[英迪拉·甘地|英迪拉·甘地]]在1971年3月27日表示她的政府全力支持東巴基斯坦人民的獨立鬥爭。稍後流亡的東巴基斯坦軍官聯合印度情報人員，開始在難民營招募及訓練解放軍游擊隊員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://im.rediff.com/news/2006/dec/14jacob.htm|title=I had to find troops for Dhaka|work=Rediff News, 14 December 2006|publisher=|accessdate=2009-10-20|archive-date=2009-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090825220726/http://im.rediff.com/news/2006/dec/14jacob.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 战争后果 ==
本次战争导致[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]脱离巴基斯坦独立。印度接受巴基斯坦提出的联合国军停战方案。

